        HERE_S_YOUR_PRESENT_A_SHINY_NEW_MOG                                     = 10990,  -- Here's your present--a shiny new Mog Safe, kupo! Now you can store as many as 60 items, kupo!
        LOOKING_AT_THAT_SHABBY_OLD_BED_MAKES_ME                                 = 10991,  -- Looking at that shabby old bed makes me feel homesick, kupo. Will my benevolent master give his/her] moogle some time off to visit with Mama and Papa Moogle, kupo?
