        IT_S_TIME_FOR_THE_EGG_HUNT_EGG                                          = 11959,  -- It's time for the Egg Hunt Egg-stravaganza, kupo! Here, take this initial egg. Collect and trade eggs until you have made a First 3 combination. When you're done, bring the combo back to me for an egg-squisite prize, kupo!
