        HEY_YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_RIGHT_YOU_RE                                   = 12284,  -- Hey! You're an adventurer, right? You're supposed to help people with stuff, right? Take this letter to that [cool guy/cute lady] in the red hat, okay?
