        WHY_JUST_YESTERDAY_I_SAW_A_CHOCOBO_SO                                   = 14405,  -- Why, just yesterday I saw a chocobo so weak, she couldn't dig a hole in a San d'Orian omelet. I swear on my grandmother's grave, Goddess bless her chocobo-loving soul.
