        AND_THAT_S_WHY_THE_BIGWIGS_DOWN_AT                                      = 14407,  -- And that's why the bigwigs down at the VCS sent me here--to help you!
        THE_CHOCOBO_HOT_AND_COLD_GAME_HAS_BEEN                                  = 14408,  -- The Chocobo Hot and Cold Game has been designed by chocobo experts from around the globe to return the pep to your noble steed's step. All you need is to love your chocobo enough to want to help it. Don't you love your chocobo?
        LET_YOUR_BIRD_TAKE_PART_IN_THE_EXCITEMENT                               = 14409,  -- Let your bird take part in the excitement, and before you know it, you'll have one lean, mean, pecking machine.
        AND_NOT_ONLY_WILL_THE_BOND_BETWEEN_YOU                                  = 14410,  -- And, not only will the bond between you and your bird become better...
        BUT_IF_YOU_RE_LUCKY_YOU_MAY_FIND                                        = 14411,  -- ...but if you're lucky, you may find yourself belly-deep in bushels of bountiful booty!
        CAN_YOU_THINK_OF_A_BETTER_WAY_TO                                        = 14412,  -- Can you think of a better way to spend a Windsday afternoon!? I know I can't!
        VCS_OFFICIALS_HAVE_BEEN_SPENDING_THE_PAST_FEW                           = 14413,  -- VCS officials have been spending the past few weeks burying chests filled with wondrous goodies in secret locations all over Vana'diel.
        ALL_YOU_HAVE_TO_DO_IS_FIND_THEM                                         = 14414,  -- All you have to do is find them, and they're yours. No strings attached!
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY                                                         = 14415,  -- What do you say?
        YOU_LOVE_YOUR_BIRD_AND_I_CAN_TELL                                       = 14416,  -- You love your bird, and I can tell by that drool trailing from the side of your mouth that you love treasure. So why not multiply the love? Love squared!
        SQUARE_YOUR_LOVE_LET_S_PLAY_NOT_TODAY                                   = 14417,  -- Square your love? Let's play. Not today.
        I_KNOW_YOU_NEED_TIME_TO_THINK_IT                                        = 14418,  -- I know, you need time to think it over. I completely understand. I guess someone else will have to find those Genbu shields that we hid...
