        WHAT_DO_YOU_NEED_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_CHOCOGRAPHS                              = 14424,  -- What do you need to know? About chocographs. About %. About how to find the loot. About chocobo abilities. About when the game is over.
        ANYONE_WHO_WANTS_TO_PARTICIPATE_IN_THE_CHOCOBO                          = 14425,  -- Anyone who wants to participate in the Chocobo Hot and Cold Game will require a special chocograph authorizing him/her] to dig in a certain area.
