        HELPING_YOUR_TEAM_INTO_FIRST_WILL_GIVE_YOU                              = 14792,  -- Helping your team into first will give you certain advantages over your rivals! That should give you something to strive for!
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_THE                                   = 14793,  -- What would you like to know about? The promenade. Chocobet centers. The grandstand. Portals. Guides. Nothing for now.
        SHOPS_AS_WELL_AS_ATTENDANTS_TO_ASSIST_YOU                               = 14794,  -- Shops, as well as attendants to assist you in siging up your chocobo for a race, are located on the promenade.
        IT_CAN_BE_FOUND_JUST_SOUTH_OF_HERE                                      = 14795,  -- It can be found just south of here.
        THE_PROMENADE_ITSELF_IS_SPLIT_INTO_EASTERN_AND                          = 14796,  -- The promenade itself is split into eastern and western halves, both of which house all of the same facilities. Be sure to stop by and have a look when you get a chance.
        ATTENDANTS_AT_THE_CHOCOBET_CENTERS_ARE_THERE_TO                         = 14797,  -- Attendants at the chocobet centers are there to assist you with acquiring %, as well as collecting your winnings.
        THERE_ARE_A_TOTAL_OF_FIVE_CENTERS_READILY                               = 14798,  -- There are a total of five centers readily available for your convenience, each of which are located near the transportation portals. There are two to the east and west of here, and one just to the north.
        ALL_CHOCOBET_CENTERS_ARE_CAPABLE_OF_PROVIDING_THE                       = 14799,  -- All chocobet centers are capable of providing the same services.
        THE_GRANDSTAND_FACES_THE_RACETRACK_ITSELF_AND_ALLOWS                    = 14800,  -- The grandstand faces the racetrack itself, and allows spectators to sit and enjoy the races in comfort.
        TO_GET_THERE_JUST_FOLLOW_THE_RED_CARPET                                 = 14801,  -- To get there, just follow the red carpet all the way through the betting area. You can't miss it.
        THE_STANDARD_ADMISSION_FEE_IS_GIL_PATRONS_WHO                           = 14802,  -- The standard admission fee is # gil. Patrons who possess % may enter free of charge.
        WILL_BE_PROVIDED_ANYTIME_YOU_PURCHASE_OR_SIGN                           = 14803,  -- % will be provided anytime you purchase % or sign up for a race.
        YOUR_WILL_BECOME_INVALID_AS_SOON_AS_YOU                                 = 14804,  -- Your % will become invalid as soon as you leave the grandstand. Reentry will require you to pay an additional admission fee.
        THIS_RACETRACK_IS_EQUIPPED_WITH_PORTALS_TO_TRANSPORT                    = 14805,  -- This racetrack is equipped with portals to transport our patrons to any of the three nations, as well as Jeuno and Al Zahbi.
        AS_YOU_CAN_SEE_WE_ARE_REGULARLY_VISITED                                 = 14806,  -- As you can see, we are regularly visited by a multitude of race fans, breeders, and jockeys from every realm imaginable. We have therefore relegated each portal to a single destination in an attempt to avoid congestion.
        FOR_THE_SAME_REASONS_WE_ASK_THAT_VISITORS                               = 14807,  -- For the same reasons, we ask that visitors refrain from setting up bazaars while here. Violators of this rule will be severely punished. Your cooperation is appreciated.
        GUIDES_CAN_BE_FOUND_THROUGHOUT_THE_PREMISES_WAITING                     = 14808,  -- Guides can be found throughout the premises waiting to assist you.
        THEY_CAN_HELP_BY_TRANSPORTING_YOU_TO_THE                                = 14809,  -- They can help by transporting you to the location of your choice.
        THIS_SERVICE_IS_PROVIDED_FREE_OF_CHARGE_SO                              = 14810,  -- This service is provided free of charge, so please don't hesitate to make use of it.
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_RACING                                = 14811,  -- What would you like to know about? Racing teams. Race rules. Race types. Victory points. Race Progression. That's about it.
        A_RACE_CHOCOBO_S_OWNER_OR_JOCKEY_MAY                                    = 14812,  -- A race chocobo's owner or jockey may join one of the three racing teams by registering at the appropriate VCS branch.
        EACH_NATION_S_TEAM_VICTORY_POINTS_ARE_THE                               = 14813,  -- Each nation's Team Victory Points are the sum total of all of its members' Solo Victory Points. The Team Victory Point totals are then used to determine the overall weekly standings.
        IN_ORDER_TO_RACE_YOUR_CHOCOBO_HERE_WE                                   = 14814,  -- In order to race your chocobo here, we ask that you please affiliate yourself first with one of the three teams.
        FOR_DETAILS_PLEASE_CHECK_WITH_YOUR_LOCAL_CRA                            = 14815,  -- For details, please check with your local CRA racing center.
        THE_RACES_HELD_HERE_ARE_ALMOST_IDENTICAL_TO                             = 14816,  -- The races held here are almost identical to the official and private races held at the other racetracks.
        WHAT_DISTINGUISHES_OUR_RACES_IS_THE_FACT_THAT                           = 14817,  -- What distinguishes our races is the fact that victories here qualify you to collect larger cash purses, as well as Victory Points.
        ELIGIBILITY_TO_PARTICIPATE_IN_THE_HIGHER_LEVEL_RACES                    = 14818,  -- Eligibility to participate in the higher-level races will require a certain number of Solo Victory Points.
        DEPENDING_ON_A_TEAM_S_WEEKLY_STANDINGS_ITS                              = 14819,  -- Depending on a team's weekly standings, its members may suffer certain eligibility restrictions. At the same time, they may also be privy to certain benefits.
        THE_TEAMS_IN_SECOND_AND_THIRD_PLACE_WILL                                = 14820,  -- The teams in second and third place will have the advantage of being allowed more entry positions in any given race, while those of the leading team are restricted.
        THE_LEADING_TEAM_WILL_HOWEVER_BE_GRANTED_THE                            = 14821,  -- The leading team will, however, be granted the privilege of selecting higher-quality saddles for their race chocobos.
        THE_CRA_RESERVES_THE_RIGHT_TO_IMPOSE_A                                  = 14822,  -- The CRA reserves the right to impose a handicap system when it is determined that the gap in skill between chocobos is simply too great to make for a fair race.
        IN_SUCH_AN_EVENT_THE_LESS_ENDOWED_OF                                    = 14823,  -- In such an event, the less endowed of the chocobos will be granted certain enhancing effects, such as Haste or Refresh.
        WHETHER_HANDICAPS_WILL_BE_ENFORCED_OR_NOT_WILL                          = 14824,  -- Whether handicaps will be enforced or not will be determined after signups are complete. Make sure to keep an eye on your chocobo's settings.
        EACH_RACE_TITLE_WILL_INCLUDE_A_CODE_SUCH                                = 14825,  -- Each race title will include a code, such as C4. This code is the race grade.
        FOR_EXAMPLE_A_C4_CHOCOBO_RACE_WOULD_INDICATE                            = 14826,  -- For example, a C4 Chocobo Race would indicate a typical grade 4 race.
        WE_HAVE_FOUR_RACE_GRADES_RANGING_FROM_C4                                = 14827,  -- We have four race grades, ranging from C4 to C1. The lower the number, the higher the grade. This, of course, means larger entry fees, but also more prize money.
        NO_MATTER_WHICH_RACE_YOU_ENTER_UPON_COMPLETION                          = 14828,  -- No matter which race you enter, upon completion you will be prevented from joining any other races for a period of 20 hours (Earth time). Higher-grade races carry larger purses, so most racers like to use their opportunities to go after those.
        SOLO_VICTORY_POINTS_WILL_BE_AWARDED_TO_YOU                              = 14829,  -- Solo Victory Points will be awarded to you every race, depending on how well you finish.
        AS_YOUR_SOLO_VICTORY_POINTS_ACCUMULATE_YOUR_CHOCOBO                     = 14830,  -- As your Solo Victory Points accumulate, your chocobo will be able to gain entry to high-grade races.
        SHOULD_A_RACER_RETURN_TO_THE_CIRCUIT_AFTER                              = 14831,  -- Should a racer return to the circuit after an absence of four weeks or more, the CRA will be forced to deduct a number of Solo Victory Points.
        ONLY_ON_THE_RAREST_OF_OCCASIONS_WILL_SUCH                               = 14832,  -- Only on the rarest of occasions will such penalties be imposed. However, there are some races in which you will be unable to participate if you do not have a certain amount of Solo Victory Points in your possession.
        ALSO_OBTAINING_SOLO_VICTORY_POINTS_WILL_ALSO_GRANT                      = 14833,  -- Also, obtaining Solo Victory Points will also grant your nation Team Victory Points.
        THE_THREE_TEAMS_ARE_IN_CONSTANT_COMPETITION_WITH                        = 14834,  -- The three teams are in constant competition with one another, and a weekly ranking system is in place based on Team Victory Point totals.
        AS_A_TEAM_CLIMBS_UP_IN_RANK_CERTAIN                                     = 14835,  -- As a team climbs up in rank, certain benefits will follow. You may see new items available for purchase with chocobucks, preferential treatment at the races, and so on.
        KEEP_IN_MIND_THAT_SHOULD_YOU_CHANGE_YOUR                                = 14836,  -- Keep in mind that should you change your team affiliation, you will be forced to forfeit any accumulated Solo Victory Points.
        WE_HAVE_A_TOTAL_OF_FOUR_RACES_THAT                                      = 14837,  -- We have a total of four races that run in succession.
        EACH_RACE_HAS_ITS_OWN_DEDICATED_SIGNUP_WINDOW                           = 14838,  -- Each race has its own dedicated signup window. Here there will be four attendants ready to serve all your racing needs.
        EVEN_IF_THE_RACE_REGISTRATION_AT_ONE_WINDOW                             = 14839,  -- Even if the race registration at one window closes, registration for the next race will begin immediately at the neighboring window.
        RACES_WILL_BE_HELD_ONE_AFTER_THE_OTHER                                  = 14840,  -- Races will be held one after the other, so you'll have plenty of chances to watch and bet. Sit back, relax, and enjoy!
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_HEAR_MORE_ABOUT                                  = 14841,  -- What would you like to hear more about? Race preparations. Signup procedure. Collecting winnings. Signing up for another race. I'm fine, thanks.
        THERE_ARE_A_FEW_FACTS_THAT_YOU_SHOULD                                   = 14842,  -- There are a few facts that you should know before running in a race.
        FIRST_OF_ALL_YOU_ABSOLUTELY_MUST_BE_AFFILIATED                          = 14843,  -- First of all, you absolutely must be affiliated with one of the three official racing teams. These, as you may already know, are San d'Oria, Bastok, and Windurst.
        SECONDLY_IT_IS_REQUIRED_THAT_YOUR_BIRD_BE                               = 14844,  -- Secondly, it is required that your bird be registered as a race chocobo, for obvious reasons. No race chocobo, no race.
        THIRDLY_YOU_WILL_BE_RESPONSIBLE_FOR_PROVIDING_YOUR                      = 14845,  -- Thirdly, you will be responsible for providing your own items to be used during the race. The CRA leaves this to the racer's discretion...
        ALL_OF_THESE_SERVICES_CAN_BE_PROVIDED_AT                                = 14846,  -- All of these services can be provided at any racing center, but to facilitate the registration process it is recommended that you conduct all such affairs at the appropriate branch.
        A_RACING_FEE_IS_NECESSARY_TO_GAIN_ENTRY                                 = 14847,  -- A racing fee is necessary to gain entry into a chocobo race. The racing center will inform you of the cost, so please be sure to pay when signing up for a race.
        ALSO_WHEN_SIGNING_UP_TO_RACE_YOU_WILL                                   = 14848,  -- Also, when signing up to race, you will be able to choose a saddle, as well as the lane in which your chocobo will race.
        THERE_ARE_MULTIFARIOUS_SADDLES_AT_THE_RIDER_S                           = 14849,  -- There are multifarious saddles at the rider's disposal, each of which will affect your chocobo's conditioning. In addition, the types of saddles available will change depending on your team's current ranking.
        THERE_ARE_A_TOTAL_OF_EIGHT_LANES_BUT                                    = 14850,  -- There are a total of eight lanes, but general conditions for all of them are the same. Feel free to race in the lane of your choice.
        SETTING_THESE_OPTIONS_WILL_COMPLETE_THE_SIGNUP_PROCESS                  = 14851,  -- Setting these options will complete the signup process. You will then be given %, which you will need to exchange later to collect any winnings.
        IN_THE_EVENT_THAT_YOU_SHOULD_LOSE_OR                                    = 14852,  -- In the event that you should lose or misplace your %, you will be unable to collect any prize money, chocobucks, or Victory Points that you may be entitled to. I cannot stress enough how important it is to hold on to it.
        THE_RACES_CAN_BE_VIEWED_FROM_OUR_GRANDSTAND                             = 14853,  -- The races can be viewed from our grandstand area. Take a seat and cheer on your bird!
        YOU_WILL_BE_ELIGIBLE_FOR_PRIZE_MONEY_IF                                 = 14854,  -- You will be eligible for prize money if your chocobo places either first, second, or third.
        TO_COLLECT_SIMPLY_HAND_IN_THE_YOU_RECEIVED                              = 14855,  -- To collect, simply hand in the % you received during race signup at any signup center.
        THE_AMOUNT_OF_GIL_CHOCOBUCKS_AND_VICTORY_POINTS                         = 14856,  -- The amount of gil, chocobucks, and Victory Points you qualify to receive will be based upon your bird's placement.
        YOU_WILL_LOSE_THE_RIGHT_TO_COLLECT_YOUR                                 = 14857,  -- You will lose the right to collect your winnings from a race exactly one week after that race has ended.
        AFTER_PARTICIPATING_IN_A_RACE_YOUR_CHOCOBO_WILL                         = 14858,  -- After participating in a race, your chocobo will be unable to join any other races for a period of 20 hours (Earth time).
        THIS_PERTAINS_ONLY_TO_RACES_HELD_HERE_AND                               = 14859,  -- This pertains only to races held here, and will not affect your eligibility for races held at any other racetracks.
        WE_HAVE_IMPLEMENTED_THESE_RESTRICTIONS_HERE_AS_TO                       = 14860,  -- We have implemented these restrictions here as to allow the greatest number of participants' entry into our races. Your patience and understanding are appreciated.
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_ASK_WHAT_IS                                      = 14861,  -- What would you like to ask? What is chocobetting? How do I bet? What are odds? When do I bet? How do I collect winnings? Nothing.
        CHOCOBETTING_IS_A_FORM_OF_ENTERTAINMENT_WHERE_BETTORS                   = 14862,  -- Chocobetting is a form of entertainment where bettors attempt to pick the two birds that will finish first and second in a race.
        TO_MAKE_IT_A_BIT_MORE_INTERESTING_THE                                   = 14863,  -- To make it a bit more interesting, the bettor can then wager on their picks in increments of 100 gil.
        SHOULD_LADY_LUCK_SMILE_UPON_YOU_AND_YOUR                                = 14864,  -- Should lady luck smile upon you and your picks hit, you can win prize money, the amount of which is determined by the odds for that race.
        FOR_EXAMPLE_LET_S_SAY_THAT_YOU_WERE                                     = 14865,  -- For example, let's say that you were to bet ten quills (1000 gil) on Entries No. 5 and No. 7.
        AND_LET_S_SAY_THAT_THE_TOTEBOARD_SHOWED                                 = 14866,  -- And let's say that the toteboard showed the odds for the race at 110 gil. If your picks were to finish as the top two birds, you would be eligible to collect 1100 gil in winnings, for a total profit of 100 gil.
        OF_COURSE_IT_GOES_WITHOUT_SAYING_THAT_SHOULD                            = 14867,  -- Of course, it goes without saying that should your picks not have the fortune of finishing in the top two places, you will receive absolutely no gil.
        THE_GAMBLER_S_FALLACY_IS_OUR_MANTRA_HERE                                = 14868,  -- The gambler's fallacy is our mantra here at the racetrack! Remember, you are special! Let it ride!
        TO_PLACE_A_CHOCOBET_YOU_MUST_OBTAIN_FROM                                = 14869,  -- To place a chocobet, you must obtain % from the chocobet center.
        FOR_ANY_SINGLE_A_BETTOR_MAY_PURCHASE_UP                                 = 14870,  -- For any single %, a bettor may purchase up to 999 quills. Each quill costs 100 gil.
        WE_HIGHLY_RECOMMEND_THAT_YOU_OBTAIN_INFORMATION_ON                      = 14871,  -- We highly recommend that you obtain information on the chocobos you will be betting on before purchasing your ticket. It is always good to know where your money is going.
        ODDS_DETERMINE_HOW_MUCH_GIL_YOU_WILL_RECEIVE                            = 14872,  -- Odds determine how much gil you will receive in winnings per quill on your chocobet ticket.
        WINNINGS_ARE_CALCULATED_BY_TAKING_THE_TOTAL_MONETARY                    = 14873,  -- Winnings are calculated by taking the total monetary sum of all bets for any given pairing. For example, should ten bettors each place the same 100-quill (10,000 gil) chocobet, the total used to determine the winnings would be 100,000 gil.
        IT_GOES_WITHOUT_SAYING_THAT_NOT_ALL_BETTORS                             = 14874,  -- It goes without saying that not all bettors will be winners. The money from losing bets is used to pay off the winners.
        WHAT_THIS_MEANS_IS_THAT_IF_YOU_PLACE                                    = 14875,  -- What this means is that if you place a bet on an unseemly chocobo pairing, or pick two birds without much money riding on them, and are fortunate enough to win, you can make quite a tidy sum.
        TOTEBOARDS_DISPLAY_THE_ODDS_AT_BOTH_THE_CHOCOBET                        = 14876,  -- Toteboards display the odds at both the chocobet center as well as the grandstand. Toteboards have eight columns with the number on top of each column representing one chocobo, and the number to the left of each column representing another. If your bet is for chocobos No. 2 and No. 5, check the #2 column to see how much a 2-5 bet will pay per quill.
        THE_ODDS_ARE_CONSTANTLY_CHANGING_RIGHT_UP_UNTIL                         = 14877,  -- The odds are constantly changing right up until the race begins. If the number of bets on a popular chocobo pairing keeps increasing, then consequently the odds will go down.
        EVEN_IF_YOU_PLACE_A_LARGE_BET_EARLY                                     = 14878,  -- Even if you place a large bet early on, the odds may still change as time passes. So take your time and consider carefully.
        CHOCOBETS_CAN_BE_PLACED_AS_SOON_AS_THE                                  = 14879,  -- Chocobets can be placed as soon as the signup period for a race has ended. The betting window will close several minutes before the race begins.
        MAKE_SURE_TO_GET_YOUR_BET_IN_ON                                         = 14880,  -- Make sure to get your bet in on time. Even if you are in the middle of placing a bet, it will be cancelled if you exceed the allowed time window by even a single second.
        ONCE_THE_RACE_IS_FINISHED_YOU_CAN_EXCHANGE                              = 14881,  -- Once the race is finished, you can exchange your % at any chocobet center to collect your winnings.
        WITHOUT_YOU_WILL_BE_UNABLE_TO_COLLECT_YOUR                              = 14882,  -- Without % you will be unable to collect your winnings, so make sure not to lose it.
        IS_VALID_FOR_UP_TO_ONE_WEEK_EARTH                                       = 14883,  -- % is valid for up to one week (Earth time) after completion of the race for which it was purchased.
        SHOULD_ONE_WEEK_PASS_WE_WILL_BE_UNABLE                                  = 14884,  -- Should one week pass, we will be unable to accept the ticket, so it is always best to cash out as soon as possible.
        ATTENTION_RACERS_SIGNUPS_FOR_THE_FOLLOWING_RACE_ARE                     = 14885,  -- Attention, racers. Signups for the following race are now open:
        PLEASE_SPEAK_WITH_THE_ATTENDANT_WEARING_UNIFORM_AND                     = 14886,  -- Please speak with the attendant wearing [an orange/a green/a red/a blue] uniform and a red beret for details. ----------
        ATTENTION_RACERS_SIGNUPS_FOR_THE_FOLLOWING_RACE_ARE_2                   = 14887,  -- Attention, racers. Signups for the following race are now closed:
