        ADVENTURER_ADVENTURER                                                   = 15457,  -- Adventurer! Adventurer!
        MIGHT_YOU_LEND_A_POOR_MOOGLE_A_HAND                                     = 15458,  -- Might you lend a poor Moogle a hand? Sure! Doing what? Not today.
        A_THOUSAND_THANKS_KUPO_YOUR_PARTICIPATION_IN_THE                        = 15459,  -- A thousand thanks, kupo! Your participation in the Neo Crystal War will benefit your nation in ways beyond imagination!
        RULES_WHY_THEY_ARE_SIMPLE_MY_FRIEND_ALL                                 = 15460,  -- Rules? Why, they are simple, my friend! All you need do is sneak your way into beastman lairs and retrieve shards from the cyclopean crystals located about the strongholds, kupo!
        WHICH_LAIRS_MUST_I_TELL_YOU_EVERYTHING_ADVENTURER                       = 15461,  -- Which lairs? Must I tell you everything, adventurer? Moogle intelligence reports that the crystals can be found in the Ghelsba Outpost, Davoi, the Palborough Mines, Giddeus, Beadeaux, and Castle Oztroja. Now what are you waiting for, kupo!?
        YOU_SEE_RECENTLY_THERE_HAS_BEEN_MUCH_UNREST                             = 15462,  -- You see, recently there has been much unrest amongst our many Moogle factions, kupo.
        WHY_YOU_ASK_WELL_AT_ONE_OF_OUR                                          = 15463,  -- Why, you ask? Well, at one of our gatherings, an argument broke out regarding the Crystal War 20 years gone.
        IT_ALL_STARTED_WITH_THE_QUESTION_WHICH_NATION                           = 15464,  -- It all started with the question: which nation played the biggest role in the allied forces' victory over the beastmen armies?
        AND_FROM_THERE_THINGS_DEGRADED_INTO_A_SHOUTING                          = 15465,  -- And from there things degraded into a shouting match pitting San d'Oria versus Bastok versus Windurst, kupo...
        HOWEVER_AT_THE_END_OF_THE_DAY_NO                                        = 15466,  -- However, at the end of the day, no one could present hard evidence to the claim of their nation's greatness.
        AND_THAT_IS_WHEN_ONE_OF_OUR_ELDERS                                      = 15467,  -- And that is when one of our elders came up with a foolproof method to put an end to our doubts--we would have adventurers from all three nations fight the war again, kupo!
        BY_FIGHTING_I_DON_T_MEAN_FIGHTING_EACH                                  = 15468,  -- By fighting, I don't mean fighting each other, but fighting the beastmen like our fathers did 20 years ago!
        ONE_OF_THE_WAYS_THE_ALLIED_ARMIES_WERE                                  = 15469,  -- One of the ways the allied armies were able to defeat the enemy was by intercepting and cutting off the Shadow Lord's crystal supply routes.
        WE_WANT_YOU_AND_OTHER_ADVENTURERS_FROM_ACROSS                           = 15470,  -- We want you and other adventurers from across Vana'diel to take on the roles of allied solders and infiltrate beastman strongholds, kupo.
        ONCE_INSIDE_YOU_ARE_TO_LOCATE_LARGE_FORMATIONS                          = 15471,  -- Once inside, you are to locate large formations where the beastmen have been storing crystals over the past two decades...
        AND_BREAK_OFF_AS_MANY_SHARDS_AS_POSSIBLE                                = 15472,  -- ...and break off as many shards as possible, then bring them back here, kupo.
        THE_NATION_THAT_BRINGS_BACK_THE_MOST_SHARDS                             = 15473,  -- The nation that brings back the most shards will be declared the Crystal War's Most Valuable Nation and the Moogles' squabbles will finally come to an end.
        SO_WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_KUPO_I_M                                             = 15474,  -- So, what do you say, kupo? I'm in. Maybe later.
