        OY_WOULD_YA_GET_A_LOOK_AT_YER                                           = 16138,  -- Oy, would ya get a look at yer %! I guess I can let ya open [/Dial 1/Dial 2/Dial 3/Dial 4/Dial 5/the special dial///the abjuration dial/the fortune dial/the furnishings dial//the Vana'versary dial/the festival dial] whenever ya want fer not a single onz o' daily tally!
